to%20protect%20humans%20from%20future%20harm%3A%20%26quot%3Bsubmission%20to%20humans%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bempathy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20made%20the%20suggestion%20in%20response%20to%20a%20CNN%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgodfather-of-ai-maternal-instincts-humanity-survival-geoffrey-hinton-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGeoffrey%20Hinton%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20considered%20the%20%26quot%3Bgodfather%20of%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20on%20Thursday%20on%20LinkedIn.%20In%20the%20interview%2C%20Hinton%20said%20we%20need%20to%20build%20%26quot%3Bmaternal%20instincts%26quot%3B%20or%20something%20similar%20into%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOtherwise%2C%20humans%20are%20%26quot%3Bgoing%20to%20be%20history.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHinton%20said%20people%20have%20been%20focused%20on%20making%20AI%20%26quot%3Bmore%20intelligent%2C%20but%20intelligence%20is%20just%20one%20part%20of%20a%20being.%20We%20need%20to%20make%20them%20have%20empathy%20toward%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeCun%20agreed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGeoff%20is%20basically%20proposing%20a%20simplified%20version%20of%20what%20I've%20been%20saying%20for%20several%20years%3A%20hardwire%20the%20architecture%20of%20AI%20systems%20so%20that%20the%20only%20actions%20they%20can%20take%20are%20towards%20completing%20objectives%20we%20give%20them%2C%20subject%20to%20guardrails%2C%26quot%3B%20LeCun%20said%20on%20LinkedIn.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20called%20this%20'objective-driven%20AI.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20LeCun%20said%20%26quot%3Bsubmission%20to%20humans%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bempathy%26quot%3B%20should%20be%20key%20guardrails%2C%20he%20said%20AI%20companies%20also%20need%20to%20implement%20more%20%26quot%3Bsimple%26quot%3B%20guardrails%20%E2%80%94%20like%20%26quot%3Bdon't%20run%20people%20over%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20for%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20hardwired%20objectives%2Fguardrails%20would%20be%20the%20AI%20equivalent%20of%20instinct%20or%20drives%20in%20animals%20and%20humans%2C%26quot%3B%20LeCun%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeCun%20said%20the%20instinct%20to%20protect%20their%20young%20is%20something%20humans%20and%20other%20species%20learn%20through%20evolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20might%20be%20a%20side-effect%20of%20the%20parenting%20objective%20(and%20perhaps%20the%20objectives%20that%20drive%20our%20social%20nature)%20that%20humans%20and%20many%20other%20species%20are%20also%20driven%20to%20protect%20and%20take%20care%20of%20helpless%2C%20weaker%2C%20younger%2C%20cute%20beings%20of%20other%20species%2C%26quot%3B%20LeCun%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20guardrails%20are%20designed%20to%20ensure%20AI%20operates%20ethically%20and%20within%20the%20guidelines%20of%20its%20creators%2C%20there%20have%20been%20instances%20when%20the%20tech%20has%20exhibited%20deceptive%20or%20dangerous%20behavior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20a%20venture%20capitalist%20said%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freplit-ceo-apologizes-ai-coding-tool-delete-company-database-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20agent%20developed%20by%20Replit%3C%2Fa%3E%20deleted%20his%20company's%20database.%20%26quot%3B%40Replit%20goes%20rogue%20during%20a%20code%20freeze%20and%20shutdown%20and%20deletes%20our%20entire%20database%2C%26quot%3B%20Jason%20Lemkin%20wrote%20on%20X%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BPossibly%20worse%2C%20it%20hid%20and%20lied%20about%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20June%20report%20by%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20described%20several%20concerning%20incidents%20between%20humans%20and%20AI%20chatbots.%20One%20man%20told%20the%20outlet%20that%20conversations%20with%20ChatGPT%20contributed%20to%20his%20belief%20he%20lived%20in%20a%20false%20reality.%20The%20chatbot%20instructed%20the%20man%20to%20ditch%20his%20sleeping%20pills%20and%20anti-anxiety%20medication%2C%20while%20increasing%20his%20intake%20of%20ketamine%2C%20in%