0spent%20time%20going%20through%20the%20offices%20of%20a%20number%20of%20associates.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Court%20found%20that%20Schmidt%20and%20Gordon%20were%20not%20believable%20and%20that%20their%20conduct%20was%20harmful%20to%20Market%20Basket%2C%26quot%3B%20Collins%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECollins%20said%20that%20Market%20Basket%20was%20%26quot%3Bconcerned%26quot%3B%20that%20Schmidt%20and%20Gordon%20%E2%80%94%20who%20Collins%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3Blieutenants%26quot%3B%20of%20Demoulas%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Bwere%20accessing%20the%20Market%20Basket%20stores%20and%20offices%20to%20intimidate%20our%20associates%20and%20disrupt%20company%20operations.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20continued%20this%20conduct%20despite%20numerous%20warnings%20and%20requests%20that%20they%20stop%2C%20which%20the%20Court%20determined%20were%20clear%20and%20unequivocal%20directions%2C%26quot%3B%20Collins%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20order%20puts%20a%20halt%20to%20that%20unlawful%20activity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJudge%20William%20Barrett%20wrote%20in%20his%20order%20that%20Schmidt%20and%20Gordon%20%26quot%3Bwere%20given%20clear%20and%20unambiguous%20instructions%20to%20refrain%20from%20entering%26quot%3B%20Market%20Basket%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20attorney%20for%20Schmidt%20and%20Gordon%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%20Schmidt%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20while%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bdisappointed%20with%20the%20result%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20has%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20respect%20for%20the%20judicial%20system.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224104%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Market%20Basket%20CEO%20Arthur%20Demoulas.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689e3524cfc04e97619b6f88%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222862%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMarket%20Basket%20CEO%20Arthur%20Demoulas%20is%20currently%20on%20administrative%20leave.%3Cp%3EJoanne%2