egseth.%20It%20said%20%26quot%3Bthe%20discussions%20clearly%20showed%20that%20the%20USA%20is%20not%20prepared%20to%20deviate%20from%20its%20position.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Swiss%20defense%20department%20was%20thus%20instructed%20to%20consider%20other%20options%20by%20the%20end%20of%20November%2C%20with%20the%20government%20saying%20the%20department%20%26quot%3Bwill%20examine%20whether%20current%20air%20defence%20requirements%20still%20correspond%20to%20the%20principles%20on%20which%20the%20evaluation%20of%20the%20F-35A%20was%20based.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222393%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close-up%20of%20the%20back%20of%20an%20F-35A%20cockpit%20as%20the%20stealth%20fighter%20comes%20in%20to%20land.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685b678385e81483682cb447%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221596%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20UK%20is%20swapping%2012%20of%20its%20F-35B%20orders%20for%20the%20F-35A%2C%20saying%20it%20wants%20to%20bring%20nuclear%20attack%20capabilities%20back%20to%20its%20air%20force.%3Cp%3EDan%20Kitwood%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELockheed%20Martin%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20%26quot%3Bsince%20foreign%20military%20sales%20are%20government-to-government%20transactions%2C%20questions%20about%20F-35%20cost%2C%20schedule%20and%20procurement%20are%20best%20addressed%20by%20the%20armasuisse%20and%20US%20government.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwitzerland%20is%20a%20neutral%20country%2C%20and%20while%20it's%20not%20a%20member%20of%20NATO%2C%20it%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20partner%20nation%20and%20has%20deepened%20its%20cooperation%20with%20the%20alliance%20since%20Russia's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20remains%20committed%20to%20the%20F-35%2C%20some%20US%20allies%20are%20no%20longer%20sure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cdc20b1b-b594-4f0e-9df8-051405aefcdb%5C%22%3ESome%20wavering%20on%20the%20F-35%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENATO%20member%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspain-rejects-f-35-for-european-alternative-continent-anxious-us-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESpain%20said%20last%20week%20that%20it%20would%20not%20buy%20the%20F-35%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20would%20instead%20focus%20on%20European%20alternatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20country's%20decision%20came%20after%20some%20other%20allies%20publicly%20questioned%20the%20fighter%20jet%20amid%20Trump's%20treatment%20of%20allies%2C%20which%20has%20included%20criticizing%20the%20NATO%20alliance%20and%20European%20defense%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20approach%20to%20the%20alliance%20and%20questions%20of%20US%20reliability%2C%20amid%20growing%20security%20concerns%2C%20has%20sparked%20a%20new%20focus%20within%20Europe%20on%20investing%20in%20the%20continent's%20defense%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPoliticians%20across%20all%20of%20Switzerland's%20political%20parties%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2025-08-07%2Fswiss-politicians-push-to-cancel-f-35-fighter-jet-deal-after-us-tariffs%3FleadSource%3Dreddit_wall%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esaid%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20the%20country%20should%20withdraw%20or%20reconsider%20its%20planned%20purchase%20of%20F-35s%20in%20response%20to%20Trump's%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226880%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22F-35A%20Lighting%20II%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66159e8a1caec1275a6e4b9f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224584%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMaj.%20Kristin%20%26quot%3BBEO%26quot%3B%20Wolfe%20demonstrates%20the%20capabilities%20of%20the%20F-35A%20Lighting%20II%2C%20a%20single%20seat%2C%20single%20engine%2C%20all-weather%20stealth%20multirole%20fighter%20aircraft%2C%20during%20a%20practice%20flight%20with%20the%20F-35%20Demonstration%20Team%20at%20Hill%20Air%20Force%20Base%2C%20Utah%2C%20Dec.%2013%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EJack%20Rodgers%2FUS%20Air%20Force%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20Spain%20is%20the%20only%20ally%20to%20formally%20step%20back%20from%20the%20jet%2C%20which%20is%20used%20by%2019%20US%20partner%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20F-35%20is%20a%20top-class%20fifth-generation%20fighter%20that%20many%20nations%20want%2C%20and%20any%20country%20that%20steps%20away%20from%20it%20after%20already%20committing%20to%20it%20would%20likely%20encounter%20huge%20costs%20and%20logistical%20issues%2C%20among%20other%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20jet's%20widespread%20use%20among%20allies%20and%20partners%20is%20also%20an%20advantage.%20It%20lets%20militaries%20operate%20together%20more%20easily%2C%20something%20that%20could%20be%20key%20in%20a%20conflict%20on%20the%20continent.%20The%20Swiss%20government%20noted%20that%20its%20desire%20for%20the%20jet%20is%20driven%20by%20how%20widespread%20F-35%20usage%20is%20across%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Europe's%20view%20of%20the%20US%20has%20changed.%20When%20asked%20on%20Wednesday%20if%20the%20US%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20reliable%20partner%20for%20future%20arms%20purchases%2C%20Pfister%20responded%20by%20saying%20that%20they%20are%20not%20reliable%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20tariffs.%20The%20depth%20of%20that%20concern%20is%20unclear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fswiterland-may-order-fewer-f-35s-over-us-pricing-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1755191091000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689de08acfc04e97619b6667%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fswiterland-may-order-fewer-f-35s-over-us-pricing-2025-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Switzerland%20said%20efforts%20to%20negotiate%20a%20fixed%20price%20for%20the%20F-35A%20jet%20were%20not%20successfu