20quest%2C%20and%20trackless%20centuries%20are%20filled%20with%20her%20striving%20and%20the%20grandeur%20of%20her%20success%20and%20her%20failures.%20Through%20good%20and%20ill%20fortune%20alike%2C%20she%20has%20never%20lost%20sight%20of%20that%20quest%20or%20forgotten%20the%20ideals%20which%20gave%20her%20strength.%20We%20end%20today%20a%20period%20of%20ill%20fortune%2C%20and%20India%20discovers%20herself%20again.%20The%20achievement%20we%20celebrate%20today%20is%20but%20a%20step%2C%20an%20opening%20of%20opportunity%2C%20to%20the%20greater%20triumphs%20and%20achievements%20that%20await%20us.%20Are%20we%20brave%20enough%20and%20wise%20enough%20to%20grasp%20this%20opportunity%20and%20accept%20the%20challenge%20of%20the%20future%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFreedom%20and%20power%20bring%20responsibility.%20The%20responsibility%20rests%20upon%20this%20Assembly%2C%20a%20sovereign%20body%20representing%20the%20sovereign%20people%20of%20India.%20Before%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F338686%2Ffreedom-fighter-gandhian-india-best-railway-minister-madhu-dandavate-rail-travel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebirth%20of%20freedom%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20have%20endured%20all%20the%20pains%20of%20labour%2C%20and%20our%20hearts%20are%20heavy%20with%20the%20memory%20of%20this%20sorrow.%20Some%20of%20those%20pains%20continue%20even%20now.%20Nevertheless%2C%20the%20past%20is%20over%2C%20and%20it%20is%20the%20future%20that%20beckons%20to%20us%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2F2_11zon-2-1754921141.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Prime%20Minister's%20words%20were%20filled%20with%20hope%20and%20ambition%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2