ming.%20%E2%80%9CI%20built%20my%20farm%20with%20an%20investment%20of%20Rs%2015%20lakh%2C%20which%20included%20building%20a%20polyhouse%20for%20Rs%208%20lakh%2C%20and%20purchasing%2012%2C000%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F277179%2Fengineer-quits-england-job-gerbera-farming-uttar-pradesh-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egerbera%20plants%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20a%20nursery%20in%20Pune%20for%20Rs%204%20lakh.%20I%20sold%20about%2040%2C000%20to%2050%2C000%20gerbera%20flowers%20per%20month%20in%20the%20Bengaluru%20market%2C%20making%20around%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20monthly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20started%20with%20gerbera%20because%20it%20was%20a%20crop%20that%2C%20if%20properly%20maintained%2C%20could%20yield%20for%20more%20than%20three%20years.%20I%20wanted%20a%20reliable%20source%20of%20income%20in%20the%20beginning%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20The%20success%20of%20this%20initial%20venture%20gave%20him%20the%20confidence%20to%20diversify%20his%20flower%20farming%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20gerberas%20proved%20to%20be%20successful%2C%20Lohith%20was%20always%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20other%20opportunities%20to%20expand%20his%20flower%20business.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20started%2C%20I%20realised%20chrysanthemum%20was%20not%20being%20grown%20much.%20Very%20few%20farmers%20were%20growing%20it%2C%20and%20the%20demand%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20that%20high.%20But%20I%20saw%20the%20potential%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20leap%20and%20started%20growing%20chrysanthemums%2C%20alongside%20gerberas.%20%E2%80%9CI%20dedicated%20around%204%2C000%20square%20meters%20of%20my%20farm%20to%20chrysanthemums%20and%20planted%202%2C000%20square%20meters%20of%20gerberas%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20His%20instinct%20to%20diversify%20paid%20off.%20Chrysanthemums%20turned%20out%20to%20have%20immense%20market%20potential%2C%20not%20just%20in%20terms%20of%20popularity%20but%20also%20because%20of%20their%20versatility%20in%20colour%20and%20size.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EExperimentation%20and%20a%20quest%20for%20quality%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20growing%20the%20flowers%20presented%20their%20own%20set%20of%20challenges.%20One%20of%20the%20major%20obstructions%20Lohith%20faced%20was%20the%20flower%E2%80%99s%20light%20sensitivity.%20%E2%80%9CChrysanthemum%20is%20a%20light-sensitive%20crop.%20It%20requires%2017-18%20hours%20of%20darkness%2C%20which%20is%20only%20possible%20during%20winter.%20Managing%20this%20in%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20longer%20summer%20days%20was%20a%20challenge%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20He%20also%20found%20that%20chrysanthemums%20grown%20in%20India%20and%20abroad%20performed%20differently%20in%20terms%20of%20quality%2C%20and%20he%20had%20to%20experiment%20with%20various%20varieties%20like%20pink%20Santini%2C%20yellow%20Santini%2C%20and%20red%20calimero%20to%20find%20the%20best%20fit%20for%20the%20local%20climate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202483px)%20100vw%2C%202483px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241220-WA0014_11zon-1735308878.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222483%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lohith%20sells%20his%20chrysanthemums%20to%20wholesalers%20and%20event%20managers%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241220-WA0014_11zon-1735308878.jpg%202483w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241220-WA0014_11zon-1735308878-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241220-WA0014_11zon-1735308878-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241220-WA0014_11zon-1735308878-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2