5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F293202%2Findependence-day-rare-pictures-of-freedom-struggle-indian-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elooking%20back%20on%20the%20remarkable%20journey%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20transformed%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20relationship%20with%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20with%20more%20than%20900%20million%20users%2C%20the%20internet%20has%20become%20an%20indispensable%20part%20of%20daily%20life%20for%20Indians.%20It%20shapes%20everything%20%E2%80%94%20from%20banking%20and%20news%20consumption%20to%20entertainment%2C%20online%20shopping%2C%20education%2C%20and%20staying%20connected%20through%20social%20media%2C%20WhatsApp%2C%20and%20video%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20internet%2C%20once%20a%20novelty%2C%20is%20now%20a%20necessity%20many%20feel%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20live%20without.%20Yet%20few%20may%20recall%20how%20this%20digital%20revolution%20began%20and%20what%20it%20took%20to%20get%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBefore%20the%20boom%3A%20BBS%20and%20the%20pre-Internet%20era%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20digital%20journey%20started%20much%20earlier%20in%20unexpected%20corners%20%E2%80%94%20often%20in%20the%20homes%20of%20passionate%20students%20and%20techies%2C%20long%20before%20commercial%20networks%20went%20live.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FSuchit-Nanda-of-Nanda-Netcom_11zon-1754993290-500x625.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22internet%20launch%20in%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FSuchit-Nanda-of-Nanda-Netcom_11zon-1754993290-500x625.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FSuchit-Nanda-of-Nanda-Netcom_11zon-1754993290-240x300.jpg%20240w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FSuchit-Nanda-of-Nanda-Netcom_11zon-1754993290-768x960.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FSuchit-Nanda-of-Nanda-Netcom_11zon-1754993290-150x188.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FSuchit-Nanda-of-Nanda-Netcom_11zon-1754993290.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-485561%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22625%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIt%20was%20in%201989%20that%20students%20Suchit%20Nanda%20and%20his%20brother%20Anish%20started%20Live%20Wire!%20BBS%20(LWBBS)%20from%20their%20bedroom%20in%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Powai.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20commercial%20internet%20arrived%20in%20India%2C%20a%20thriving%20BBS%20(Bulletin%20Board%20System)%20community%20existed%2C%20connecting%20computers%20over%20landlines%20and%20modems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%201989%20that%20students%20Suchit%20Nanda%20and%20his%20brother%20Anish%20started%20Live%20Wire!%20BBS%20(LWBBS)%20from%20their%20bedroom%20in%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Powai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELWBBS%20was%20the%20first%20and%20largest%20BBS%20in%20the%20Indian%20subcontinent%2C%20playing%20a%20foundational%20role%20in%20connecting%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F180422%2Fpaytm-movie-tickets-internet-handling-fees-rbi-vijay-gopal-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearly%20Indian%20internet%20users%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20fostering%20a%20digital%20community%20before%20internet%20access%20became%20widespread.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20BBS%20became%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20and%20largest%2C%20connecting%20users%20nationwide%20through%20the%20global%20FidoNet%20network.%20This%20led%20to%20my%20participation%20in%20INET%20conferences%2C%20where%20I%20advocated%20for%20public%20internet%20access%20in%20India.%20Given%20the%20security%20policies%20then%2C%20only%20government-linked%20bodies%20could%20launch%20the%20internet.%20VSNL%20was%20ideal%2C%20as%20it%20had%20existing%20lease%20lines%20and%20global%20partnerships.%20This%20led%20to%20meetings%20with%20VSNL%E2%80%99s%20leadership%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20internet%20revolution%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Suchit%20Nanda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENanda%E2%80%99s%20pioneering%20spirit%20didn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20at%20advocacy.%20His%20tech%20firm%20was%20among%20the%20first%20to%20receive%20an%20internet%20licence%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Telecommunications%20(DoT).%20He%20played%20a%20trailblazing%20role%20in%20expanding%20digital%20access%20through%20the%20development%20of%20internet%20set-top%20boxes%20(STBs)%20%E2%80%94%20bringing%20the%20web%20to%20television%20screens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20innovative%20ventures%20like%20Nanda%20Netcom%20and%20Jadoonet.com%2C%20in%20collaboration%20with%20tech%20giants%20Samsung%20and%20Intel%2C%20he%20helped%20make%20the%20internet%20more%20accessible%20to%20Indian%20households%2C%20redefining%20how%20people%20connected%20and%20consumed%20digital%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20launch%3A%20VSNL%E2%80%99s%20gateway%20to%20the%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Independence%20Day%20in%201995%2C%20the%20GIAS%20public%20internet%20service%20by%20VSNL%20was%20launched%20and%20opened%20to%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FNeeraj-Sonker-Pic-Coutesy-constl.com_11zon-1754993300-500x533.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22internet%20launch%20in%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FNeeraj-Sonker-Pic-Coutesy-constl.com_11zon-1754993300-500x533.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FNeeraj-Sonker-Pic-Coutesy-constl.com_11zon-1754993300-281x300.jpg%20281w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FNeeraj-Sonker-Pic-Coutesy-constl.com_11zon-1754993300-768x818.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FNeeraj-Sonker-Pic-Coutesy-constl.com_11zon-1754993300-150x160.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FNeeraj-Sonker-Pic-Coutesy-constl.com_11zon-1754993300.jpg%201080w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-485562%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22533%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20beginning%2C%20dial-up%20capacity%20was%20limited%20to%20just%2016%20or%2032%20lines%2C%20and%20we%20had%20access%20to%20only%20four%20Class%20C%20IP%20addresses%20from%20APNIC%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20Neeraj%20Sonker%2C%20who%20served%20as%20General%20Manager%2C%20Internet%20Services%20at%20VSNL%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20then%2C%20the%20internet%20in%20India%20was%20only%20available%20to%20educational%20and%20research%20institutes%20via%20ERNET%20(the%20first%20internet%20connection%20to%20India)%2C%20NICNET%20(for%20government%20only)%2C%20and%20STP%20(for%20tech%20parks%20only).%20The%20public%20internet%20service%20was%20a%20milestone.%20The%20GIAS%20launch%20was%20just%20the%20start%20%E2%80%94%20it%20opened%20the%20floodgates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBehind%20the%20scenes%3A%20pioneers%20and%20partnerships%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20helped%20shape%20the%20backend%20systems%20and%20rollout%20strategy%2C%20using%20our%20experience%20running%20a%20nationwide%20BBS%20network.%20A%20close%20group%20of%20tech%20leaders%20and%20system%20admins%20%E2%80%94%20like%20Atul%20Chitnis%2C%20Kishore%20Bhargava%2C%20and%20others%20%E2%80%94%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20turning%20the%20vision%20into%20reality.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20outset%2C%20the%20internet%20launch%20covered%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20cities%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Mumbai%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Chennai%2C%20Kolkata%2C%20and%20Pune.%20A%20couple%20of%20weeks%20later%2C%20Bangalore%20was%20added%20to%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERetail%20customers%20received%20dial-up%20services%2C%20while%20enterprises%20were%20offered%20leased%20line%20connections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20beginning%2C%20dial-up%20capacity%20was%20limited%20to%20just%2016%20or%2032%20lines%2C%20and%20we%20had%20access%20to%20only%20four%20Class%20C%20IP%20addresses%20from%20APNIC%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20Neeraj%20Sonker%2C%20who%20served%20as%20General%20Manager%2C%20Internet%20Services%20at%20VSNL%20from%201994%20to%202000%2C%20in%20a%20LinkedIn%20post%20marking%20the%20silver%20jubilee%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20internet%20launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EScaling%20up%3A%20from%20metro%20cities%20to%20tier%202%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F139241%2Fvoip-calls-clearer-internet-telecom-sync-ist%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Department%20of%20Telecommunications%20(DoT)%20%3C%2Fa%3Edirected%20VSNL%20to%20extend%20internet%20services%20to%20Tier%202%20cities%2C%20beginning%20with%20state%20capitals.%20Starting%20in%201996%2C%20VSNL%20began%20rolling%20out%20internet%20access%20across%20these%20regional%20hubs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESonkar%E2%80%99s%20account%20of%20the%20period%20provides%20insights%20into%20the%20technical%20and%20operational%20challenges%20faced%2C%20including%20scaling%20infrastructure%20to%20meet%20skyrocketing%20demand%20and%20addressing%20customer%20and%20media%20criticism%20in%20the%20early%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20highlights%20how%2C%20despite%20limited%20network%20expertise%20and%20resources%2C%20the%20team%20managed%20to%20connect%20major%20cities%20through%20a%2064-kbps%20satellite%20link%2C%20established%20Points%20of%20Presence%20(POPs)%20across%20India%2C%20provided%20dial-up%20and%20leased%20line%20services%2C%20and%20later%20expanded%20the%20network%20to%20Tier%202%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20leadership%20also%20saw%20the%20rollout%20of%20key%20innovations%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20the%20shift%20from%20static%20to%20dynamic%20network%20routing%20and%20improvements%20in%20customer%20support%20and%20billing%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEmpowering%20users%3A%20The%20internet%20guide%20and%20community%20building%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20team%20continued%20to%20upgrade%20infrastructure%20and%20expand%20services%2C%20attention%20increasingly%20turned%20to%20empowering%20customers%20to%20navigate%20the%20new%20digital%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20pivotal%20initiative%20in%20this%20direction%20was%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20Internet%20User%20Guide%20(The%20Guide)%2C%20which%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20boon%20for%20both%20customers%20and%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecognising%20the%20need%20for%20user%20empowerment%2C%20the%20team%2C%20at%20Nanda%E2%80%99s%20suggestion%2C%20enlisted%20Stanford%20Professor%20Dr%20Raj%20Mehta%20to%20craft%20the%20Internet%20User%20Guide.%20Dr%20Mehta%E2%80%99s%20hands-on%20approach%20%E2%80%94%20fielding%20late-night%20calls%20and%20emails%20from%20users%20nationwide%20%E2%80%94%20reflected%20the%20spirit%20of%20collaboration%20at%20the%20dawn%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20digital%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Mehta%20returned%20to%20India%20during%20that%20time%20and%20dedicated%20significant%20effort%20to%20assisting%20VSNL%20and%20end-users.%20In%201997%2C%20the%20spiral-bound%20book%20was%20published.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px